WEBVTT

00:00.285 --> 00:02.269
You will need to find
the Book of Leaves.

00:02.270 --> 00:03.955
And you are closer every day.

00:04.022 --> 00:06.991
Lorenzo makes an embassy
to the Duke of Urbino.

00:08.729 --> 00:09.830
Brilliant!

00:09.898 --> 00:12.567
He seeks to create a
new military alliance.

00:12.635 --> 00:14.395
It's too long since I
led my men into combat.

00:14.437 --> 00:16.539
Our proposal
is timely indeed.

00:16.607 --> 00:18.408
End the House of Medici.

00:18.475 --> 00:20.342
Before I end you.

00:20.410 --> 00:22.410
Those caught roaming
the streets after curfew

00:22.478 --> 00:24.245
get put in my little book.

00:24.313 --> 00:26.322
Anyone who breaks curfew,
for the slightest reason,

00:26.347 --> 00:27.382
will be put down here.

00:27.383 --> 00:30.151
Including the true spy whom you
believe framed Becchi.

00:30.219 --> 00:32.354
You've seen what happens
when people question

00:32.421 --> 00:35.056
the plans of the Vatican,
haven't you?

00:35.123 --> 00:38.025
Giuliano, you'd make a
fine husband for Camilla.

00:39.027 --> 00:40.261
The key.

00:40.329 --> 00:42.463
It's waiting in Rome.

00:42.530 --> 00:45.532
Your mother,
she's alive.

